Victor J. EVANS, Appellant, v. UNITED STATES of America, Appellee. No. 11457. Circuit Court of Appeals, Fifth Circuit. Dec. 18, 1945. No appearance for appellant. H. S. Phillips, U. S. Atty., and D. New-comb Barco, Jr., Assti U. S. Atty., both of Tampa, Fla., and Damon G. Yerkes, Asst. U. S. Atty., of Jacksonville, Fla., for ap-pellee.
